Almost everyone I mentioned her to doesn't even remember seeing her in Aquaman. ie. She's very forgettable. She's not a good actress and doesn't have chemistry with Jason Mamoa. At best, she's an easily replaceable, random chicky with no personality.  
Her acting talent is only good enough for the WWE. Only a brainless and irrelevant company would choose easily forgettable Amber Turd over truly talented and memorable Johnny Depp! The only explanation I can think of is that this succubus is prostituting herself to someone at Warner Bros. I used to think well of Warner Bros.
